00:45:36,330 --> 00:45:37,890
Mgube先生
Mr.Mgube.

654
00:45:37,970 --> 00:45:40,170
- 带来了? - 对
- You have it? - Yeah.

655
00:45:41,570 --> 00:45:43,370
你准备好钱了?
Do you have the money?

656
00:45:48,530 --> 00:45:52,490
说好的50万英镑
500,000,as agreed.

657
00:45:54,890 --> 00:45:58,970
- 另外50万呢? - 你同事又没来
- And the extra 50,000? - Your colleague is no longer with you.

658
00:46:00,410 --> 00:46:02,290
那我就连他那份也要了
Which means I get his share.

659
00:46:10,650 --> 00:46:11,720
钞票呢
The note.

660
00:46:55,610 --> 00:46:56,930
给他
Pay the man.

661
00:47:00,530 --> 00:47:03,210
跟你做生意真是愉快
It's been a real pleasure doing business with you gents.

662
00:47:14,050 --> 00:47:16,970
- 你们在干大买卖 - 我觉得
- Something's going on. - I reckon...

663
00:47:18,530 --> 00:47:19,850
应该就是现在了
about now.

664
00:48:05,170 --> 00:48:07,480
- 我能帮你吗? - 我找Foster女士
- Can I help you? - I'm here to see Mrs.Foster.

665
00:48:07,570 --> 00:48:10,250
- 谁? - Foster女士 她住这的
- Who? - Mrs.Foster,she lives here.

666
00:48:10,490 --> 00:48:12,610
- 不是啊 没这个人 - 那你是谁
- No,she doesn't. - So,who the hell are you?

667
00:48:12,690 --> 00:48:15,410
我住这里的 这是我的房子啊
I live here,this is my house.

668
00:48:15,490 --> 00:48:18,530
- 什么? - 我们刚放假回来
- What? - We've just come back off holiday.

669
00:48:29,810 --> 00:48:33,010
- 怎么样 Betty? - 还是该叫你Foster女士?
- How'd we do,Betty? - Or should we call you Mrs.Foster?

670
00:48:33,530 --> 00:48:35,890
15万
150,000.

671
00:48:36,290 --> 00:48:38,250
- 不是吧 - 这么多
- You're joking. - No way.

672
00:48:38,330 --> 00:48:40,640
我们想最多就2万 2万5
We only had him down for 20,000,25,000 tops.

673
00:48:40,730 --> 00:48:43,010
看来这小家伙全付身家放进去了
Seems the little shit was holding out on you.

674
00:48:43,090 --> 00:48:47,450
我们也猜想他会有些钱的
Well,that's what we thought he had stashed in the caravan,but....

675
00:48:47,530 --> 00:48:50,050
他也没让我们失望
Seems he came into a small windfall.

676
00:48:56,530 --> 00:48:57,890
喂?
Hello?

677
00:48:59,290 --> 00:49:00,440
对了
Yeah,it is.

678
00:49:08,850 --> 00:49:11,050
我们的银行经理
Our favorite bank manager...

679
00:49:11,130 --> 00:49:13,690
买下了他的旅行车
must have bought his worthless caravan...

680
00:49:13,770 --> 00:49:17,080
和他那块地
and even more worthless land for....

681
00:49:19,170 --> 00:49:21,530
15万啊?
150,000 in cash.

682
00:49:32,690 --> 00:49:36,160
我想问一下 停车场的土建工程谁中标了?
Yes,I'm trying to find out who's won the car parking franchise...

683
00:49:36,250 --> 00:49:38,480
就是那个Portway Estate 公司的开发项目
for the new development on the Portway Estate?

684
00:49:39,930 --> 00:49:41,690
什么没有?那个开发项目啊
What do you mean,"what development"?

685
00:49:43,450 --> 00:49:45,170
给我转去 规划局
Let me talk to the Planning Officer.

686
00:50:10,970 --> 00:50:12,930
教你一招
Here's the note.

687
00:50:13,010 --> 00:50:16,010
最重要的是要做的好像有点紧张似的
The most important thing,all right,is to look a bit nervous...

688
00:50:16,090 --> 00:50:17,920
就像我们知道我们不该去
like we know we shouldn't be there.

689
00:50:19,690 --> 00:50:22,080
他也知道我们这样做会丢了工作的
He knows what we're doing could cost us our jobs.

690
00:50:22,170 --> 00:50:24,450
就让他这样想吧
Let's make him think he's doing all the running.

691
00:50:24,530 --> 00:50:26,410
- 好了 - 你准备好了?
- Right. - You ready?

692
00:50:28,010 --> 00:50:29,890
有什么问题
What's wrong?

693
00:50:30,570 --> 00:50:32,560
- 不是吧 不见了 - 什么意思 他不见了
- Oh,no.It's gone. - What do you mean,it's gone?

694
00:50:34,090 --> 00:50:36,160
好了好了 对不起
Oh,yeah.All right.Sorry.

695
00:50:58,610 --> 00:51:00,570
我真不相信你们不等我就开始了
I can't believe you started without me.

696
00:51:04,330 --> 00:51:06,160
我能租一辆房车吗?
Yeah,can I hire a limousine?

697
00:51:07,170 --> 00:51:08,970
我叫Mgube
In the name Mgube.

698
00:51:09,290 --> 00:51:10,570
真经典
It's traditional.

699
00:51:10,650 --> 00:51:13,960
是属于Nigerian的...
Yes,it's sort of Nigerian...

700
00:51:14,050 --> 00:51:15,450
你知道的
you know,yeah.

701
00:51:15,970 --> 00:51:20,360
12件白衬衫 16条衣领 还有些领带
Twelve white shirts,16 collar,and a dozen assorted ties.

702
00:51:20,970 --> 00:51:22,120
打扮
Perks.

703
00:51:26,810 --> 00:51:29,170
除了白的还是白的 觉得怎么样
It's white or white.What do you reckon?

704
00:51:29,250 --> 00:51:31,560
- 我觉得 - 我也会选白的
- Well,I think.... - Yeah,I thought white myself.

705
00:51:31,650 --> 00:51:33,370
- 白的? - 对啊
- White? - Yeah.

706
00:51:35,250 --> 00:51:39,330
说好50万
500,000 as agreed.

707
00:51:57,170 --> 00:51:59,210
你知道Stacie是怎么做的吗?
Did you hear about Stacie's little contribution?

708
00:51:59,290 --> 00:52:02,050
- 我知道 - 厉害 我自己也要赞一下自己
- Oh,yeah. - Brilliant,even if I do say so myself.

709
00:52:09,730 --> 00:52:11,930
- 你要我站哪? - 前面吧
- Where do you want me,Mick? - Out front.

710
00:52:14,250 --> 00:52:15,890
看他来不来
I wish I could see his face.

711
00:52:28,490 --> 00:52:31,050
- 有什么可以帮你? - 怎么回事?
- Can I help you,sir? - What's going on?

712
00:52:31,610 --> 00:52:34,370
- 封了 - 为什么
- It's been closed down. - What for?

713
00:52:34,810 --> 00:52:35,800
不知道
I don't know.

714
00:52:36,330 --> 00:52:40,210
CID找到了一个犯罪团伙 可能是骗子吧
CID just dragged a gang out of there.Con men I reckon.

715
00:52:42,570 --> 00:52:45,960
- 你跟这有关系吗? - 没有
- Do you have any business here,sir? - No.

716
00:52:46,370 --> 00:52:47,850
那 走吧
Move along,then.

717
00:53:07,650 --> 00:53:10,610
- Eddie 你好像看糊涂了 - 对啊 你们怎么就没糊涂
- Eddie,you look confused. - Well,wouldn't you be?

718
00:53:10,690 --> 00:53:11,730
让我解析一下
Yeah,well,let me explain.

719
00:53:11,810 --> 00:53:14,170
不 别告诉我 我不想知道
No!Don't tell me,'cause I don't even wanna know.

720
00:53:14,570 --> 00:53:16,850
真不知道你们是什么想的
Wonder where that little weasel's sleeping tonight.

721
00:53:16,930 --> 00:53:19,570
好了 我们至少没把他的车也骗走啊
Yeah,well,at least we let him keep his van.

722
00:53:20,770 --> 00:53:24,450
对啊 我们不是不能做到喔
Yeah,we did.We should have had that as well.

723
00:53:24,530 --> 00:53:28,080
- 他自己找来的 - 把我们骗子的名声都搞臭了
- He had it coming to him. - Giving honest con men a bad name.

724
00:53:28,410 --> 00:53:30,170
你怎么找到他的?
Where did you find the little creep?

725
00:53:30,610 --> 00:53:32,810
不是拉 应该算是他找我们的
Well,he found us,kind of.

726
00:53:32,970 --> 00:53:34,410
我不明白
I don't get it.

727
00:53:34,490 --> 00:53:37,090
我估计他以前就只会骗骗老人家罢了
I reckon he's been fleecing little old ladies his whole life.

728
00:53:40,090 --> 00:53:44,560
- Rice先生在吗? - 那是我先生
- Good morning,darling.Mr.Rice? - That's my husband.

729
00:53:44,650 --> 00:53:46,560
他在吗?有个包裹给他的
Is he in?I've got a parcel for him.

730
00:53:46,850 --> 00:53:49,320
- 他去世了 - 对不起
- He passed away. - Oh,I'm sorry.

731
00:53:49,450 --> 00:53:54,210
- 我能代领喔 - 货到付款 75英镑
- I can take it. - It's cash on delivery and it's 75.

732
00:53:54,610 --> 00:53:55,650
那是什么啊?
But what is it?

733
00:53:55,730 --> 00:53:58,090
我想这是你先生生前
I guess what I'm holding here was most likely the last thing...

734
00:53:58,170 --> 00:54:00,560
最后订的一件东西吧
your husband ordered before he passed away.

735
00:54:00,770 --> 00:54:04,370
- 好了 我拿回去好了 - 等一下 我去拿钱包
- Listen,don't you worry,I'll take it back. - No,wait.I'll get my purse.

736
00:54:04,490 --> 00:54:05,480
好的
Okay.

737
00:54:42,930 --> 00:54:45,320
但他选错了对象
But then he made a very big mistake.

738
00:54:45,490 --> 00:54:47,720
他居然搞到我奶奶头上了
He picked on the wrong little old lady.

739
00:54:51,650 --> 00:54:53,010
奶奶
Nan!

740
00:54:53,970 --> 00:54:55,200
唉 亲爱的
Hello,darling.

741
00:54:55,290 --> 00:54:57,010
我们把他骗倒了 搞定了
We got him.Yeah,we did.

742
00:54:57,090 --> 00:55:00,240
告诉你 他再也不敢去搞你了 你可是我们的荣誉嘉宾啊
I tell you what,he's never gonna con you again and you're our guest of honor.

743
00:55:00,330 --> 00:55:02,400
- 我没怎么出来玩 - 是吗?
- Oh,I don't get out much. - Don't you?

744
00:55:02,490 --> 00:55:04,320
那个司机人很好的
The taxi driver was very nice.

745
00:55:04,410 --> 00:55:06,370
是吧 你没跟他乱说什么吧?
Was he now,you weren't chatting him up,were you?

746
00:55:06,450 --> 00:55:09,050
- Daniel! - 我就知道你爱那么干
- Oh,Daniel! - I know what you old girls are like.

747
00:55:09,450 --> 00:55:12,210
好的了 你要什么 来杯香槟吧
All right,what do you fancy?A little glass of champagne?

748
00:55:12,290 --> 00:55:14,760
香槟?那我会整晚都很high的
Champagne?Oh,I'll be up all night.

749
00:55:14,850 --> 00:55:15,970
你会整晚都很high 不是因为香槟
You will be up all night...

750
00:55:16,050 --> 00:55:19,010
因为你会跟你最喜爱的孙子跳舞
'cause you're gonna be dancing with your favorite grandson.

751
00:55:19,130 --> 00:55:20,850
来吧 我们来跳
Let's have it,come on.

752
00:55:23,290 --> 00:55:27,490
听着 Mickey 你能帮我把钱存到银行吗?
Listen,Mickey,can I pay the money into the bank?

753
00:55:27,570 --> 00:55:29,450
- 所有? - 对啊
- All of it? - Yeah.

754
00:55:29,530 --> 00:55:33,320
我就想看那Hopkins
I just want to watch Hopkins counting his money...

755
00:55:33,410 --> 00:55:35,170
把自己的钱存入我们的帐户
into our account.

756
00:55:35,250 --> 00:55:37,640
你可能有点变态 你得注意点
There is a very wicked streak in you,do you know that?

757
00:55:37,730 --> 00:55:40,040
我要这样做才心理平衡啊
Well,there's nothing quite like getting even.

758
00:55:40,130 --> 00:55:41,450
没事的
Nothing at all.

759
00:55:46,370 --> 00:55:47,360
谢谢你Stacie.
Thanks,Stacie.

760
00:55:49,210 --> 00:55:53,890
来干一杯吧 敬爷爷一杯吧 奶奶
How about a little toast,then?Here's to Granddad,Nan.

761
00:55:55,690 --> 00:55:56,680
干杯
Cheers.

762
00:56:07,530 --> 00:56:10,610
- 说真的 Eddie 你真厉害 - 我不要听
- Really,Eddie,you have been fantastic. - I'm not listening.

763
00:56:10,850 --> 00:56:12,410
- 为什么 - 因为你会骗我钱的
- Why? - 'Cause you'll take money off me.

764
00:56:12,490 --> 00:56:14,640
- 你怎么这样说 - 因为你的确会骗我的
- How can you say that? - Because you do.

765
00:56:14,730 --> 00:56:16,050
Eddie
Eddie.

766
00:56:16,570 --> 00:56:19,130
好的 我听你说 但我这次是不会再开钱箱的了
All right,I'll listen,but I'm not opening that till.

767
00:56:19,210 --> 00:56:24,130
好的 那很公平啊 我给你露一手
Well,okay,yeah,fair enough.Hey,I've gotta show you this.

768
00:56:24,450 --> 00:56:27,650
你猜我多久能喝完三大杯白兰地?
How long do you think it'll take me to drink three large brandies?

769
00:56:27,850 --> 00:56:29,410
看你多渴罗
Depends how thirsty you were.

770
00:56:30,330 --> 00:56:32,210
- 不要一秒 - 不可能
- Under a second. - No way.

771
00:56:32,370 --> 00:56:33,360
那赌多少
Yeah,how much?

772
00:56:33,570 --> 00:56:36,010
不 我说了 我怎么也不会再开那钱箱的了
No,I've told you,there's no way I'm opening that till.

773
00:56:36,090 --> 00:56:37,530
好的 就玩玩
Okay,for fun,then.

774
00:56:38,050 --> 00:56:39,570
- 玩玩 - 是的
- Fun? - Absolutely.

775
00:56:39,930 --> 00:56:42,050
- 不赌钱? - 不赌
- No money? - No.

776
00:56:42,650 --> 00:56:45,170
- 好的 - 好的
- Okay. - Okay.

777
00:56:45,250 --> 00:56:46,240
斟酒吧
Set them up.

778
00:56:57,130 --> 00:57:01,570
- 不用一秒? - 对 不用一秒
- Under a second? - Yep,under a second.

779
00:57:04,650 --> 00:57:07,170
- 我计时 - 好 没问题
- I'll do the timing. - Yeah,agreed.

780
00:57:09,490 --> 00:57:12,850
- 你说开始就开始 - 开始
- Say when. - Go.

781
00:57:13,090 --> 00:57:15,480
停 你输了
Stop!You lose!

782
00:57:17,410 --> 00:57:18,690
好咧
Yes!

783
00:57:29,650 --> 00:57:31,250
你别再这样干拉
Will you stop doing that,please?

784
00:57:31,330 --> 00:57:33,010
就是拉 跟人家一样付钱买单啊
Yeah,pay for your drinks like everyone else.

785
00:57:34,610 --> 00:57:36,410
祝Eddie.
To Eddie.

786
00:57:36,490 --> 00:57:38,770
干杯Eddie 谢谢
Cheers,Eddie,thank you!

